From bb119b06181e56e9055a7a86185022375d2a7158 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Saravanakumar Duraisamy <saradura@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Sun, 6 Jul 2025 16:11:35 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] QSDK:PLATFORM:wifi: ath12k: Add QDSS support

- Add QDSS qmi handling infra to ath_debug module
- Moved QDSS dump collection support to ath_debug module
- ath12k coredump ops registration to ath_debug module

Usage:
echo 1 >
/sys/kernel/debug/ath12k/<device>/ath_debug/qdss/enable
echo 1 >
/sys/kernel/debug/ath12k/<device>/ath_debug/qdss/collect

e.g.
1 > /sys/kernel/debug/ath12k/ahb-c000000.wifi/ath_debug/qdss/enable
QDSS:
0x01 > /sys/kernel/debug/ath12k/ahb-c000000.wifi/ath_debug/qdss/collect
PHYA0:
0x40 > /sys/kernel/debug/ath12k/ahb-c000000.wifi/ath_debug/qdss/collect
PHYA1:
0x80 > /sys/kernel/debug/ath12k/ahb-c000000.wifi/ath_debug/qdss/collect

Signed-off-by: Saravanakumar Duraisamy <saradura@qti.qualcomm.com>
